Her high jump won her the gold medal.

meanings.definition: feeling or showing pleasure or contentment

meanings.definition: to mark (letters, words, or other symbols) on a surface

meanings.definition: of a size that is less than normal or usual

meanings.definition: to move (a door, window, etc.) so that an entrance, passage, or space becomes accessible

meanings.example: The store is open for business.

meanings.definition: the natural agent that stimulates sight and makes things visible

meanings.definition: free from dirt, marks, or stains

meanings.definition: to make something free of dirt

meanings.definition: moving or capable of moving at high speed

meanings.definition: to construct by putting parts or materials together
